<tr>
  <td style="padding-bottom: 10px">
    Welcome to the NOGIC JQS (Nigerian Oil and Gas Industry Content Joint
    Qualification System) Portal, <%= org_name %>
  </td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td style="padding-bottom: 10px">
    In line with Section 55 of the Nigerian Oil and Gas Industry Content
    Development Act, the Nigerian Oil and Gas Industry Content Joint
    Qualification System has been set up by the board as an electronic platform
    to consolidate data on activities of stakeholders in the Industry.
  </td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td style="padding-bottom: 10px">
    Please note that a portal account profile has been created for your
    organization on the Nigerian Oil and Gas Industry Content Joint
    Qualification System (NOGIC JQS) Portal (<a href="https://novasphere.gov.ng"
      >https://novasphere.gov.ng</a
    >).
  </td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td style="padding-bottom: 10px">
    <strong>These are your login credentials:</strong>
  </td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td style="padding-bottom: 10px">
    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="50%">
      <tr>
        <td>Email Address:</td>
        <td><%= email %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Password:</td>
        <td><%= password %></td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td style="padding-bottom: 10px">Thank You.</td>
</tr>
